    "body": "When I run Lerna commands, i.e. `lerna list`, I get the following warning.\r\n\r\n```\r\nConfiguring yargs through package.json is deprecated and will be removed in a future major release, please use the JS API instead.\r\nConfiguring yargs through package.json is deprecated and will be removed in a future major release, please use the JS API instead.\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\nNo yargs warning\r\n\r\n## Current Behavior\r\nyargs warning is present\r\n\r\n<details><summary>lerna.json</summary><p>\r\n<!-- browsers demand the next line be empty -->\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"npmClient\": \"yarn\",\r\n  \"packages\": [\"packages/*\"],\r\n  \"useWorkspaces\": true,\r\n  \"version\": \"independent\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n</p></details>\r\n\r\n## Your Environment\r\n<!--- Include as many relevant details about the environment you experienced the bug in -->\r\n\r\n| Executable | Version |\r\n| ---: | :--- |\r\n| `lerna --version` | 3.16.5 |\r\n| `npm --version`  | 6.10.3 |\r\n| `yarn --version` | 1.19.1 |\r\n| `node --version` | v10.16.1 |\r\n\r\n| OS | Version |\r\n| --- | --- |\r\n| macOS Catalina | 10.15 |",
